title: READERS DISCUSS: Desire to see flights to Sydney, Melbourne
text:
JETGO is currently running three services a week on the new route, but managing director Paul Bambereck said they would soon be looking to expand as demand increases. 
We asked readers via Facebook: Where would you like to see Jetgo fly to from Rockhampton? 
Peter McDonald - Rocky to Melbourne. Rocky to Cairns. 
Sheena Elliott - Rocky to Melbourne would be fantastic. 
Morgan Hasan - Rocky to Sydney. Rocky to Melbourne. 
Brenda Mooney - All the best fantastic you are including the Gold Coast. 
Kellie Evans - Rocky Adelaide. Rocky cairns. 
Jodie Marie - Rocky to Sydney. 
Lyn Dumesny - Rocky to Melbourne please. 
Judy Cornick - Rocky to Sydney. 
Breanna Smith - Rocky to Melbourne. 
Erin Smith - Rocky - sydney. Rocky - melbourne. Rocky - adelaide. Rocky - perth. Rocky - darwin. 
Tamara Spilsbury - DIRECT flights from Rocky to Sydney. Always stopping over in Brisbane is hard when you're traveling with small children. Rocky to Wollongong would be even better for me, but there won't be any demand for that. 
Chantal Booth - all the capitals please. AND Alice. 
Renee McCrea - Rocky to Melbourne. 
Jimmi Foord - ROK-SYD direct. 
Bronwyn Welburn - Rocky to sydney. 
Debbie Bryant - Great news. 
Chris Dickinson - Gold Coast to Rocky. flights
